<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Order Confirmation - <b>My</b>Profile</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            box-sizing: border-box !important;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif !important;
            background: transparent !important;
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 10px !important;
            min-height: 100vh !important;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            background: #ffffff !important;
            border-radius: 16px !important;
            overflow: hidden !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) !important;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            color: white !important;
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0 !important;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            margin: 0 auto 16px !important;
            display: block !important;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            object-fit: contain !important;
            display: block !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
        }
        
        .order-card {
            background: #f0fdf4 !important;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0 !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            padding: 20px !important;
            margin: 25px 0 !important;
        }
        
        .order-item {
            display: flex !important;
            justify-content: space-between !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            padding: 12px 0 !important;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb !important;
        }
        
        .order-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none !important;
        }
        
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block !important;
            padding: 12px 24px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            margin: 15px 0 !important;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f8f8 !important;
            padding: 25px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0 !important;
        }
        
        .support-link {
            display: inline-flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 6px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            padding: 10px 16px !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            margin-bottom: 12px !important;
            font-size: 13px !important;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .header {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .order-card {
                padding: 15px !important;
            }
            
            .order-item {
                flex-direction: column !important;
                align-items: flex-start !important;
                gap: 8px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 10px; min-height: 100vh; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;">
    <div class="email-container" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);">
        <div class="header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; color: white; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;">
            <div class="logo" style="width: 45px; height: 45px; margin: 0 auto 16px; display: block;">
                <img src="cid:company-logo" alt="<b>My</b>Profile Logo" style="width: 45px; height: 45px; object-fit: contain; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
            </div>
            <h1 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.2; color: white;">âœ… Order Confirmed</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; font-weight: 400; color: white;">Thank you for your order</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content" style="padding: 30px 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568;">
                Thank you for your order! We've received your order and it's being processed. Here are your order details:
            </p>
            
            <div class="order-card" style="background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    ðŸ“¦ Order #{{orderNumber}}
                </h3>
                
                <div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 10px;">Order Details:</h4>
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Order Date:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">{{formatDate orderDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Status:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #16a34a;">{{orderStatus}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Estimated Delivery:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">{{formatDate estimatedDelivery}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin: 20px 0 10px;">Items Ordered:</h4>
                {{#each orderItems}}
                <div class="order-item" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">{{name}}</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">Qty: {{quantity}}</div>
                        {{#if description}}
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px;">{{description}}</div>
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: right;">
                        <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">${{price}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
                
                <div style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Subtotal:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">${{subtotal}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{#if shipping}}
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Shipping:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">${{shipping}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if tax}}
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 5px 0;">
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Tax:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">${{tax}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                        <span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Total:</span>
                        <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #166534;">${{total}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if shippingAddress}}
            <div style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 10px;">ðŸšš Shipping Address:</h4>
                <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.4;">
                    {{shippingAddress.name}}<br>
                    {{shippingAddress.street}}<br>
                    {{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}} {{shippingAddress.zipCode}}<br>
                    {{shippingAddress.country}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="action-button" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    ðŸ“¦ Track Your Order
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; margin-bottom: 8px;">ðŸ“‹ What's Next:</h4>
                <ul style="font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.4; margin-left: 15px;">
                    <li>You'll receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking details</li>
                    <li>Your order will be processed within 1-2 business days</li>
                    <li>Estimated delivery: {{formatDate estimatedDelivery}}</li>
                    <li>Questions? Contact our support team anytime</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 20px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; text-align: center;">
                Thank you for choosing <b>My</b>Profile! We appreciate your business.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer" style="background: #f8f8f8; padding: 25px 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <a href="mailto:support@getmyprofile.online" class="support-link" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 13px;">
                ðŸ“§ Contact Support
            </a>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.5;">
                This is an automated message from <b>My</b>Profile. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
                If you need assistance, please contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 